# Alina Automation Python Projects

This repository contains my training and practical projects from the **QA Automation Python** course.  
The focus is on **UI automation (Selenium + POM), API testing (Requests + Pytest), Docker, PostgreSQL and Jenkins CI/CD**.

> Note: Folder names like `lesson_30`, `lesson_31` etc. come from the course structure.  
> Below you can find where the main projects are located.

